  "text" : {
    "status" : "generated",
    "div" : "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: Requirements zw-lab-result-pull</b></p><a name=\"zw-lab-result-pull\"> </a><a name=\"hczw-lab-result-pull\"> </a><p>These requirements apply to the following actors: </p><ul><li><a href=\"ActorDefinition-lab-result-consumer.html\">Lab Result Consumer</a></li><li><a href=\"ActorDefinition-lab-result-repository.html\">Lab Result Repository</a></li></ul><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b><a name=\"result-pull-01\"> </a></b>Result search</td><td>SHALL</td><td><div><p>The Lab Result Repository SHALL support searching DiagnosticReport by <code>subject</code>/<code>patient</code> and by <code>based-on</code>, returning <code>searchset</code> Bundles whose entries conform to <a href=\"StructureDefinition-zw-lab-diagnostic-report.html\">ZWLabDiagnosticReport</a>.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b><a name=\"result-pull-02\"> </a></b>Report document retrieval</td><td>SHALL</td><td><div><p>The Lab Result Repository SHALL allow retrieval of stored report documents (Bundle read/search by <code>identifier</code>) as submitted by the Lab Result Provider.</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><b><a name=\"result-pull-03\"> </a></b>Order correlation</td><td>SHOULD</td><td><div><p>The Lab Result Consumer SHOULD correlate retrieved results back to the originating order it placed (ServiceRequest/Task) for display against the request.</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
  },
